// Root Project Folder: charm-companion

charm-companion/
├── public/
│   └── assets/
│       └── mods/                  # Requiem mod images
│       └── qrcodes/              # QR exports (optional)
│       └── fashion/              # User screenshots (optional)
├── src/
│   ├── assets/
│   │   └── icons/                # Faction icons, resources, loadout symbols
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── calendar/             # Full calendar UI system
│   │   ├── clans/                # Clan creation/joining tools
│   │   ├── events/               # Thermia, Ghoul Purge, etc trackers
│   │   ├── goals/                # Goal setting and tracking tools
│   │   ├── guides/               # Guides reader/editor
│   │   ├── home/                 # Homepage tiles and alert boxes
│   │   ├── import/               # ScannerJsonUpload.tsx
│   │   ├── lfg/                  # Blessing trains, group finder
│   │   ├── lichtracker/          # Mod table, logic, suggestion system
